| **Edge** | No supernatural power. Collective > individual. Warriors fight mage's stamina. |
| **Realms** | Each hides a secret. Each fears Order discovery. All are trapped. |
| **Artifacts** | Category Five does not officially exist. Debt-nulls break the rules. |
| **Pressure** | Five active crisis points. Any could break the Order's monopoly. |

